---
import { site, url } from "../lib/data";
---

<section class="bg-paper py-8 md:py-16">
  <div class="container-x">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-y-10 md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-x-16">
      <div class="md:col-span-7">
        <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[2px] bg-elevated md:aspect-[5/4]">
          <img
            src={site.images.atmosphere}
            alt=""
            width="1200"
            height="1400"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover"
          />
          <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tl from-brand/15 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-5 md:self-center">
        <p class="eyebrow mb-5">Cabinetul</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-[30px] leading-[1.15] tracking-tight text-ink md:text-[40px]">
          Un loc liniștit, gândit pentru pacient.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-prose text-[16px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
          Lumină naturală, scaune confortabile, fără publicitate pe pereți. Cabinetul nostru este organizat în jurul unei idei: timpul tău aici trebuie să fie cât mai puțin tensionat.
        </p>
        <a href={url("/despre")} class="mt-7 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[15px] font-medium text-brand hover:text-brand-deep">
          Vezi de ce ne aleg pacienții
          <svg width="14" height="10" viewBox="0 0 14 10" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M0 5H12.5M8 1L13 5L8 9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
